  <div>
   <p xml:id="1" begin="00:00:00.501" end="00:00:02.970">SCHOOL, OUT MARCH 28TH.</p>
   <p xml:id="2" begin="00:00:02.303" end="00:00:04.872">AND MUCH MORE.</p>
   <p xml:id="3" begin="00:00:03.104" end="00:00:06.808">THAT BOOK IS ON ITS WAY TO YOU.</p>
   <p xml:id="4" begin="00:00:05.006" end="00:00:07.375">FINALLY TONIGHT, THE FACTOR &quot;TIP</p>
   <p xml:id="5" begin="00:00:06.941" end="00:00:08.776">OF THE DAY.&quot;</p>
   <p xml:id="6" begin="00:00:07.508" end="00:00:09.911">CONSIDER THIS, A MAN BOOKS A</p>
   <p xml:id="7" begin="00:00:08.910" end="00:00:12.113">FLIGHT FOR A BABY AND HIMSELF ON</p>
   <p xml:id="8" begin="00:00:10.044" end="00:00:14.048">A MAJOR AIRLINE.</p>
   <p xml:id="9" begin="00:00:12.247" end="00:00:15.516">HE ATTEMPTS TO HOLD THE CHILD ON</p>
   <p xml:id="10" begin="00:00:14.182" end="00:00:16.317">HIS LAP WHICH YOU CAN DO IF THE</p>
   <p xml:id="11" begin="00:00:15.650" end="00:00:18.586">BABY IS UNDER TWO YEARS OLD</p>
   <p xml:id="12" begin="00:00:16.451" end="00:00:20.388">WHICH SHE WAS AT THE TIME OF</p>
   <p xml:id="13" begin="00:00:18.720" end="00:00:23.091">BOOKING.</p>
   <p xml:id="14" begin="00:00:20.521" end="00:00:24.392">BUT NOT ON THE DAY OF FLIGHT.</p>
   <p xml:id="15" begin="00:00:23.224" end="00:00:29.931">THE TICKET AGENT TELLS THE MAN</p>
   <p xml:id="16" begin="00:00:24.525" end="00:00:29.264">HE HAS TO PONY UP 749     $749 T</p>
   <p xml:id="17" begin="00:00:29.264" end="00:00:29.631">HE HAS TO PONY UP 749     $749 O</p>
   <p xml:id="18" begin="00:00:29.631" end="00:00:29.664">HE HAS TO PONY UP 749     $749 G</p>
   <p xml:id="19" begin="00:00:29.664" end="00:00:29.731">HE HAS TO PONY UP 749     $749 T</p>
   <p xml:id="20" begin="00:00:29.731" end="00:00:29.764">HE HAS TO PONY UP 749     $749 O</p>
   <p xml:id="21" begin="00:00:29.764" end="00:00:30.298">HE HAS TO PONY UP 749     $749 N</p>
   <p xml:id="22" begin="00:00:30.064" end="00:00:33.434">THE PLANE.</p>
   <p xml:id="23" begin="00:00:30.431" end="00:00:34.702">HE CANNOT AFFORD IT.</p>
   <p xml:id="24" begin="00:00:33.568" end="00:00:37.538">SUDDENLY, ANOTHER PASSENGER WHO</p>
   <p xml:id="25" begin="00:00:34.836" end="00:00:38.139">WAS HEARING THIS STEPS UP AND</p>
   <p xml:id="26" begin="00:00:37.672" end="00:00:43.211">BUYS THE BABY A TICKET.</p>
   <p xml:id="27" begin="00:00:38.273" end="00:00:48.182">A COMPLETE STRANGER.</p>
   <p xml:id="28" begin="00:00:43.344" end="00:00:49.951">AFTER AN INVESTIGATION, WAY TO</p>
   <p xml:id="29" begin="00:00:48.316" end="00:00:52.086">GO, MISS BOLTON.</p>
   <p xml:id="30" begin="00:00:50.084" end="00:00:53.755">I BELIEVE THE AIRLINE SHOULD</p>
   <p xml:id="31" begin="00:00:52.220" end="00:00:54.322">HAVE ISSUED THE BABIES TICKET</p>
   <p xml:id="32" begin="00:00:53.888" end="00:00:55.156">GRATIS.</p>
   <p xml:id="33" begin="00:00:54.455" end="00:00:59.294">I ALSO BELIEVE THAT DEBBIE</p>
   <p xml:id="34" begin="00:00:55.290" end="00:00:59.894">BOLTON IS A PATRIOT.</p>
  </div>
